dct_title_s: Telephone lines used by Dirkzwager's Ship Agency in connection with those of Holland-Belgium, France and Germany
dct_description_sm: Upper map shows telephone lines in Belgium, Holland, and parts of France and Germany; lower map shows telephone lines from the Hook of Holland to Rotterdam.
